{"title":"淡水情","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":6,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"淡水情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港的淡水呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血液般的珍贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸有祖国母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常可紧紧地依偎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水管似条条血管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通向干渴的体内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯净的流注赛醇酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不汲不饮也心醉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感受着温馨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品味着甘美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"觉得每一个细胞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都能萌发出花蕾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔日饮水思源，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入肠化作相思泪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日饮水思亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为庆回归齐干杯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杯中淡水水不淡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓情厚意久萦回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更增生命的张力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活的情味……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：四川作协）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}